00:40:59.402 --> 00:41:01.963
they are fewer than one in a million,

00:41:02.043 --> 00:41:05.588
set apart as they are each unto Yahowah.

00:41:06.329 --> 00:41:08.190
Even when purified in white,

00:41:08.411 --> 00:41:11.934
all become beautiful in Leah's elegant

00:41:11.994 --> 00:41:12.434
attire.

00:41:13.277 --> 00:41:16.599
such that they can still be fragile after

00:41:16.639 --> 00:41:17.159
their birth.

00:41:17.199 --> 00:41:19.202
If someone stomps on them or grabs them

00:41:19.262 --> 00:41:22.364
too firmly or permanently tries to yank

00:41:22.385 --> 00:41:22.925
them away,

00:41:22.965 --> 00:41:26.367
they can melt and lose everything that had

00:41:26.467 --> 00:41:28.989
once made them special.

00:41:29.050 --> 00:41:31.851
So they have to be protected at least

00:41:31.891 --> 00:41:34.815
for a while until they are ready to

00:41:34.855 --> 00:41:37.336
mature and to be part of something greater

00:41:37.376 --> 00:41:39.057
than themselves.

00:41:39.599 --> 00:41:42.101
When this happens and they do grow,

00:41:42.903 --> 00:41:45.065
Leah will adorn them in crimson,

00:41:46.385 --> 00:41:49.327
the crimson revealing their royal status.

00:41:50.728 --> 00:41:56.911
But also, both Dowd, her son, and Baal,

00:41:57.472 --> 00:41:58.152
her husband,

00:41:59.373 --> 00:42:01.253
are known for being adorned in red.

00:42:02.954 --> 00:42:06.117
Yashayah later will tell us that the man

00:42:06.157 --> 00:42:09.559
from Edom is properly attired and he is

00:42:09.659 --> 00:42:11.519
festooned in red.

00:42:12.641 --> 00:42:14.300
not only for having coming out of the

00:42:14.340 --> 00:42:14.942
wine vat,

00:42:15.422 --> 00:42:17.822
but because he will be sacrificed,

00:42:18.541 --> 00:42:20.503
as was Dowd on a Mowedym.

00:42:21.342 --> 00:42:22.083
So Dowd,

00:42:22.543 --> 00:42:24.704
after conveying the stains of his

00:42:24.764 --> 00:42:25.523
ineptitude,

00:42:25.583 --> 00:42:27.463
making him bright and white again,

00:42:27.884 --> 00:42:30.324
he was prepared to be bathed in scarlet

00:42:30.385 --> 00:42:31.324
red, finally,

00:42:31.364 --> 00:42:33.385
depicting his service as the Passover

00:42:33.445 --> 00:42:33.766
lamb.

00:42:34.985 --> 00:42:38.606
It's a rite of passage portrayed as a

00:42:38.666 --> 00:42:39.626
sojourner in time.

00:42:42.188 --> 00:42:44.108
More than this, as Yahowah's Amah,

00:42:44.268 --> 00:42:46.550
productive mother and seamstress,

00:42:46.751 --> 00:42:51.034
Leah is offering what I once attributed to

00:42:51.054 --> 00:42:52.054
the Ruwach spirit,

00:42:52.155 --> 00:42:56.597
a garment of luminosity that covers our

00:42:56.617 --> 00:43:00.280
shame and makes us appear pure as the

00:43:00.300 --> 00:43:01.019
driven snow.

00:43:02.141 --> 00:43:04.222
And with the reference to crimson,

00:43:05.210 --> 00:43:07.753
It is offered in collaboration with her

00:43:07.813 --> 00:43:11.275
sons and her husband's fulfillment of the

00:43:11.295 --> 00:43:11.856
Mowedym.

00:43:12.436 --> 00:43:14.177
Boy, a mother of many sorrows.

00:43:16.018 --> 00:43:18.561
This is how we grow and mature in

00:43:18.601 --> 00:43:19.601
the covenant family,

00:43:20.362 --> 00:43:22.744
from the unique fragility and purity of a

00:43:22.824 --> 00:43:26.927
snowflake to an adult adorned by our king

00:43:27.608 --> 00:43:30.369
and his mother.

00:43:30.429 --> 00:43:33.152
Well, to quote the great Dr. Seuss,

00:43:34.326 --> 00:43:34.405
Oh,

00:43:34.445 --> 00:43:36.907
the things we can think when only we

00:43:36.947 --> 00:43:38.887
try.

00:43:39.007 --> 00:43:41.347
And mother, father, husband,

00:43:41.387 --> 00:43:46.449
and son are nowhere near concluding this

00:43:46.568 --> 00:43:46.969
lesson.

00:43:47.869 --> 00:43:49.768
There are more things to think.

00:43:52.389 --> 00:43:59.552
She makes coverings and fabrics for her of

00:44:00.532 --> 00:44:01.072
fine linen.

00:44:04.115 --> 00:44:08.057
in addition to woven wool, yarn,

00:44:08.117 --> 00:44:12.480
and cloth for her garments.

00:44:12.500 --> 00:44:16.422
Proverbs thirty-one, twenty-two.

00:44:16.442 --> 00:44:18.682
We're back to this garment of luminosity.

00:44:18.762 --> 00:44:24.005
We're back to adorning the king to purify

00:44:24.065 --> 00:44:25.567
his appearance before Yahowah,

00:44:26.367 --> 00:44:29.248
but also as the one who would fulfill

00:44:29.628 --> 00:44:30.168
Pesach,

00:44:31.414 --> 00:44:34.514
And then once again in the royal line,

00:44:35.655 --> 00:44:39.956
but with the fine textiles of linen,

00:44:40.436 --> 00:44:42.516
which means she will attire him for

00:44:43.518 --> 00:44:45.878
fulfilling Yowm Kipurym,

00:44:45.978 --> 00:44:48.079
the day of reconciliations as the high

00:44:48.119 --> 00:44:50.679
priest in the linen apparel.

00:44:51.400 --> 00:44:51.940
And of course,

00:44:52.760 --> 00:44:56.461
