because of a corruption of it by a

00:45:38.851 --> 00:45:43.835
bunch of meddlesome and perverted women

00:45:45.556 --> 00:45:46.376
was true all along.

00:45:47.597 --> 00:45:49.239
There really is a garment of luminosity.

00:45:50.539 --> 00:45:53.422
It is the apparel of our mother.

00:45:54.523 --> 00:45:56.744
And it is the garment that is going

00:45:56.764 --> 00:45:58.186
