00:46:16.679 --> 00:46:19.141
So there really is a maternal aspect to

00:46:19.201 --> 00:46:19.840
all of this.

00:46:20.900 --> 00:46:23.581
And there really is a garment of

00:46:23.621 --> 00:46:26.322
luminosity and it is crafted

00:46:27.202 --> 00:46:30.304
of the finest coverings and fabrics,

00:46:30.684 --> 00:46:34.628
particularly of fine linen and woven wool

00:46:34.688 --> 00:46:35.128
yarn.

00:46:35.650 --> 00:46:38.331
Again, linen and wool,

00:46:39.172 --> 00:46:41.054
primarily because in this context,

00:46:41.094 --> 00:46:43.936
