he did and appreciation for what he did

00:49:04.043 --> 00:49:05.684
and be sympathetic of how difficult the

00:49:05.724 --> 00:49:07.385
job is that he's been asked to do.

00:49:07.425 --> 00:49:10.148
A lamb is a flock animal,

00:49:10.429 --> 00:49:11.590
and you want to be part of that

00:49:11.630 --> 00:49:11.989
flock.

00:49:12.871 --> 00:49:14.371
It's also a quite intelligent flock

00:49:14.391 --> 00:49:14.672
animal.

00:49:14.692 --> 00:49:15.512
Yes, of course.

00:49:15.733 --> 00:49:16.773
Yeah, they are.

00:49:17.454 --> 00:49:17.753
But they're...

00:49:18.695 --> 00:49:20.856
probably the most congenial of all animals

00:49:20.916 --> 00:49:23.438
in terms of wanting it to not only

00:49:23.478 --> 00:49:25.280
be with their person and to be led

00:49:25.360 --> 00:49:27.503
and cared for and protected by a person

00:49:28.163 --> 00:49:30.164
but also being together among the

00:49:30.224 --> 00:49:32.726
community so it's a it's a marvelous way

00:49:33.467 --> 00:49:37.010
of presenting Dowd and of uh of

00:49:37.690 --> 00:49:39.452
ElYah, he is presented as the goat,

00:49:39.992 --> 00:49:40.952
as the woolly goat,

00:49:41.132 --> 00:49:42.474
because he's a bit raw.

00:49:42.775 --> 00:49:44.275
A little less approachable.

00:49:44.295 --> 00:49:45.697
And he's, you know,

00:49:45.976 --> 00:49:48.318
he'll say whatever it comes to mind.

00:49:49.438 --> 00:49:54.862
And he was like a goat, more independent.

00:49:56.847 --> 00:49:59.650
And so it it shows his independence.

00:49:59.690 --> 00:50:03.512
It shows his kind of woolly nature as

00:50:03.552 --> 00:50:06.835
a as a man and the fact that

00:50:06.856 --> 00:50:08.277
