way.

01:19:56.265 --> 01:19:57.885
It is always Yada Yada.

01:20:02.713 --> 01:20:05.154
So this affirms that the place where I

01:20:05.194 --> 01:20:06.215
will be, Yada,

01:20:06.536 --> 01:20:11.858
acknowledged as such is Baha Sha'ar,

01:20:12.257 --> 01:20:14.618
within the inter-sanctum of the thoughtful

01:20:14.658 --> 01:20:15.118
assembly.

01:20:16.019 --> 01:20:17.560
That means that everybody who is part of

01:20:17.579 --> 01:20:20.081
the covenant going forward will have thunk

01:20:20.121 --> 01:20:22.521
themselves into that position.

01:20:22.841 --> 01:20:25.662
You come to know God up here.

01:20:26.103 --> 01:20:28.644
That's the point Leah has been making to

01:20:28.684 --> 01:20:30.585
Dowd from the beginning.

01:20:30.885 --> 01:20:31.685
Think your way through.

01:20:32.046 --> 01:20:32.286
Mm-hmm.

01:20:32.926 --> 01:20:37.230
This is inside the door that Dowd opened

01:20:37.431 --> 01:20:39.953
on Pesach for the covenant family to life.

01:20:40.435 --> 01:20:42.756
It is also apparent based upon the king's

01:20:42.817 --> 01:20:46.420
prophetic pronouncement that known as both

01:20:46.541 --> 01:20:49.604
Baal and Yada, that I will Yashab,

01:20:50.043 --> 01:20:52.546
dwell and remain among the Zaqen,

01:20:53.186 --> 01:20:55.770
the elders of the material realm.

01:20:57.421 --> 01:21:00.742
So while this is Leah's story,

01:21:02.042 --> 01:21:04.641
she did not happen upon it alone.

01:21:05.403 --> 01:21:09.042
The Amah has a Baal named Yada,

01:21:10.144 --> 01:21:13.003
and he has an interesting role to play

01:21:13.083 --> 01:21:15.585
in Yahowah's story too.

01:21:15.685 --> 01:21:17.284
Indeed.

01:21:18.204 --> 01:21:19.765
As I have shared,

01:21:19.926 --> 01:21:22.185
ours is unarranged marriage.

01:21:23.694 --> 01:21:26.496
It's true.

01:21:26.515 --> 01:21:27.716
There is no way around that.

01:21:28.277 --> 01:21:28.676
I know.

01:21:30.358 --> 01:21:30.478
Yeah.

01:21:30.497 --> 01:21:34.219
I was so against anything remotely of that

01:21:34.298 --> 01:21:36.060
kind, but yeah, it is.

01:21:38.121 --> 01:21:39.600
It's an arranged marriage.

01:21:39.621 --> 01:21:42.362
Yahowah sent her to me, uh,

01:21:42.381 --> 01:21:45.604
by email letter, uh,

01:21:46.604 --> 01:21:47.904
asking the same question.

01:21:47.923 --> 01:21:49.164
So who do you think you are?

01:21:49.244 --> 01:21:49.364
Yep.

01:21:50.619 --> 01:21:51.760
And as you recall,

01:21:51.840 --> 01:21:52.740
but it's still in my mind.

01:21:52.801 --> 01:21:53.940
Why are you doing what you're doing?

01:21:54.001 --> 01:21:54.400
Yes.

01:21:54.582 --> 01:21:54.782
Yep.

01:21:55.202 --> 01:21:57.302
She was searching for Yahowah,

01:21:58.143 --> 01:22:01.404
and God told her at the time that

01:22:01.543 --> 01:22:04.784
she would find what she was seeking if

01:22:04.824 --> 01:22:06.805
she went to ask Ruwth.

01:22:07.265 --> 01:22:08.247
Yep.

01:22:08.287 --> 01:22:08.966
Go ask Ruwth.

01:22:09.106 --> 01:22:09.367
Yeah.

01:22:10.287 --> 01:22:10.747
She did.

01:22:11.047 --> 01:22:13.068
Now, we're an hour and a half.

01:22:13.287 --> 01:22:13.809
Go ask.

01:22:13.969 --> 01:22:14.969
Eighteen-year quest.

01:22:15.048 --> 01:22:15.729
Go ask Ruwth.

01:22:16.510 --> 01:22:18.350
I'm looking forward because it is such an

01:22:18.470 --> 01:22:20.011
interesting episode with Ruwth.

01:22:21.159 --> 01:22:23.641
to beginning our next program with this.

01:22:24.381 --> 01:22:26.764
So we're going to take a break.

01:22:26.844 --> 01:22:30.546
We'll do another round of the last word

01:22:30.605 --> 01:22:33.306
picture, the final Mashal tomorrow.

01:22:34.307 --> 01:22:37.310
And we'll resume with what Leah would have

01:22:37.390 --> 01:22:40.872
read when Yahowah told her to go ask

01:22:41.032 --> 01:22:44.793
Ruwth and how that takes us right back

01:22:45.673 --> 01:22:47.735
to where we are and everything we have

01:22:47.796 --> 01:22:48.275
just read.

01:22:49.737 --> 01:22:50.877
So thank you so much,

01:22:51.137 --> 01:22:53.380
master of the cables.

01:22:54.001 --> 01:22:56.884
I appreciate your contribution when asked

01:22:56.944 --> 01:22:57.724
as you punted the...

01:22:59.021 --> 01:23:00.042
the fall earlier,

01:23:00.523 --> 01:23:01.743
I think I would have done the same

01:23:01.783 --> 01:23:02.043
thing.

01:23:02.923 --> 01:23:04.585
We look forward to being with you both.

01:23:04.604 --> 01:23:07.426
We'll do another episode tomorrow,

01:23:08.627 --> 01:23:09.886
perhaps in the Rainbow Studio,

01:23:09.926 --> 01:23:11.127
perhaps the Ocean Studio,

01:23:11.167 --> 01:23:13.868
followed by one here again in our library

01:23:13.908 --> 01:23:16.911
studio in the pursuit of our understanding

01:23:17.131 --> 01:23:18.771
of the last word picture.

01:23:18.792 --> 01:23:19.032
Good day.